path of exile api info


some api info
https://www.reddit.com/r/pathofexiledev/comments/7aiil7/how_to_make_your_own_queries_against_the_official/

get leagues

https://www.pathofexile.com/api/trade/data/leagues


To search send a POST request to https://www.pathofexile.com/api/trade/search/YOUR_LEAGUE with a json object containing your query. A super simple one searching for The Pariah on Standard would look like this.

 
POST: https://www.pathofexile.com/api/trade/search/Standard
	{
	    "query": {
	        "status": {
	            "option": "online"
	        },
	        "name": "The Pariah",
	        "type": "Unset Ring",
	        "stats": [{
	            "type": "and",
	            "filters": []
	        }]
	    },
	    "sort": {
	        "price": "asc"
	    }
	}



all items: https://www.pathofexile.com/api/trade/data/items
all stats: https://www.pathofexile.com/api/trade/data/stats


